    <string name="credits_title">Credits</string>
    <string name="credits_body">ClimaPilot\'s local Midea protocol is a Kotlin port of the excellent midea-msmart project by @mill1000. Huge thanks — without it this app wouldn\'t exist.</string>
    <string name="credits_link">midea-msmart on GitHub</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_5_title">Version 0.5</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_5_body">•  New: Weekly day-planner — assign scenes to recurring weekday + time windows (e.g. max cooling on Mondays, 6–18) on a visual week calendar; off or keep-running at the end\n•  Runs in the background even while the phone is idle on Wi-Fi (Doze-proof), survives reboots\n•  Note: while a plan is active Android shows the alarm-clock icon; for reliable timing allow background use under Settings ▸ Reliable timers</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_4_2_title">Version 0.4.2</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_4_2_body">•  Fixed: the all-in-one home-screen widget failed to load (\"Problem loading widget\")\n•  IR remote: added Swing, Quiet, Turbo and Eco toggles — it now also remembers its last state\n•  Fan speed: added a 1% quick preset</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_4_1_title">Version 0.4.1</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_4_1_body">•  New: IR-remote mode (infrared) — control the AC like a remote on phones with an IR blaster, no Wi-Fi needed\n•  Fixed: the app could not be updated over an earlier version (the app signing key was restored)</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_4_title">Version 0.4</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_4_body">•  New tabbed navigation: Control · Options · Scenes · Status · History — adapts to a side rail on tablets and in landscape\n•  Energy &amp; filter history with charts — power, indoor/outdoor temperature and fan level, by hour / day / week / month or a chosen day, per AC; optional background recording every ~15 min (Wi-Fi)\n•  Wear OS companion app — control the AC from your watch\n•  Reliable off/sleep timer — retries, survives a reboot, with a live countdown notification (off now / cancel)\n•  Auto power-off after a maximum runtime\n•  App lock with fingerprint or PIN\n•  Mode tile for Quick Settings · launcher shortcuts (off / scene / demo)\n•  “Reliable timers” setup helper (battery optimisation &amp; manufacturer auto-start)\n•  Redesigned ON/OFF slider and more compact mode &amp; fan controls</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_3_2_title">Version 0.3.2</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_3_2_body">•  Fixed a crash when starting the sleep timer on some devices (e.g. Xiaomi/HyperOS)</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_3_1_title">Version 0.3.1</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_3_1_body">•  Sleep timer now powers the AC off on time even when the app is closed and the phone is idle (Doze)</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_3_title">Version 0.3</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_3_body">•  Fixed: a saved device could appear twice after a search\n•  Fixed: the sleep timer now powers the AC off even when the app is closed\n•  Widgets reorganised by function: separate power, temperature &amp; mode widgets + a redesigned all-in-one widget\n•  Mode widget: pick any mode directly from chips (active one highlighted) instead of cycling\n•  All-in-one widget redesigned: centered power button, connection light, temperature &amp; mode chips</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_2_title">Version 0.2</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_2_body">•  Quick scenes with full editor &amp; daily schedule\n•  Live status: power, total consumption &amp; estimated cost\n•  Options: swing, eco, beep — plus ionizer, outdoor-silent &amp; self-clean where the unit supports them\n•  Compressor throttle; sleep timer with custom, saved durations\n•  Offline token caching — internet only on the first connect; export &amp; import tokens\n•  Saved devices for instant offline reconnect\n•  Reorder the control cards via the drag handle\n•  Home-screen widget in 1×1 / 2×2 / 4×2 (power, temperature, mode) + Quick Settings tile\n•  °C/°F switch and price per kWh</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_1_title">Version 0.1</string>
    <string name="changelog_0_1_body">•  Initial release\n•  Local control of Midea air conditioners over Wi-Fi\n•  Mode, temperature, fan, swing, eco &amp; beep\n•  Live status: indoor/outdoor temperature, power, consumption, error code\n•  Quick scenes &amp; sleep timer\n•  Compressor throttle\n•  Demo mode without a device</string>

